### Local Variables Configuration (Machine-Specific Overrides)
# This is an example file. Copy it to 01-local-variables.conf and customize for your machine.
# Any variable defined here will override the default from 00-variables.conf
# The actual 01-local-variables.conf file is gitignored to keep your personal settings private.

# Example: Override display names for a different machine
# set $laptop eDP-2
# set $external DP-1

# Example: Override wallpaper paths for this specific machine
# set $wallpapers ~/Pictures/MyWallpapers

# Example: Use different default applications
# set $term kitty
# set $browser chromium
# set $filemanager thunar

# Example: Different color scheme for this machine
# set $bg_color #1a1b26
# set $fg_color #c0caf5
# set $focused_bg #7aa2f7
# set $focused_fg #1a1b26
